1 Import des donnes et configuration de lenvironnement de travail

1.1 Chargement des librairies

library(data.table)
library(ggplot2)
library(wordcloud)
library(wordcloud2)

1.2 Chargement des donnes

# on charge les donnes
dataset = readRDS(here::here("output","mots.rds"))

2 Nuage de mot

# without mask
wordcloud(words = dataset$word, 
          freq = dataset$freq, 
          # min.freq = quantile(dataPlot$n,0.75),
          # max.words=200, 
          random.order=FALSE, 
          rot.per=0.35, 
          scale=c(2.5,0.25)*1.4,
          colors=brewer.pal(8, "Dark2"))
